                            "body": "I believe there are a couple of errors in the description and code: r should be divided by the squared magnitude of P1P2, not the magnitude of PP1. Haven&#39;t checked the math, but that&#39;s consistent with the answer linked to in the comment by @hatchet, and that works much better!"
